data.description:
Welcome to this stunning, meticulously maintained CBS home, surpassing new construction, built in 2020. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a den, 2-car garage, and room for all the toys.  This residence offers an array of luxurious features from the moment you step through its grand covered entrance.The heart of this home lies in its exquisite kitchen, showcasing custom-built shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, sleek black stainless steel appliances, a center island, and a pantry. The expansive great room is accentuated by a tray ceiling, a contemporary electric fireplace, and sliding glass doors that lead to the recently constructed top-of-the-line screened-in pool (completed in 2023) and lanai. Enjoy relaxation and entertainment in the pool featuring a sun shelf and a hot tub The versatile den can easily serve as a fourth bedroom, while the private master suite is a sanctuary for homeowners. Revel in the tray ceiling, dual walk-in closets, French doors opening to the lanai, and serene backyard views. Pamper yourself in the spa-like master bathroom with dual vanities, a separate tub, and a walk-in shower.

Noteworthy features include hurricane impact doors and windows, an indoor laundry room, 8-foot interior doors throughout, two gated long driveways, plenty of covered space to store a boat, rv or any of your toys, and an impressive 26 x 60 hurricane-rated detached building, ideal for storage or hobbies. This additional space boasts a 12-foot front door, a 10-foot side rolling door, a 26 x 20 exterior overhang, and a 10 x 60 covered side slab.

Outside, the home is equipped with an extra electrical panel and drainage for a potential summer kitchen. The fenced yard is adorned with Areka Palms, garden beds with irrigation, a fire pit, and a top-of-the-line water filtration system by Allure Water Systems. Additionally, the septic system was serviced in 2024.

Situated in desirable Jupiter, Florida, on a paved road, this residence offers convenience with easy access to I95, the turnpike, beaches, upscale shopping, dining, and Excellent A-rated schools. Enjoy the benefits of cable, 5G high-speed internet availability, and ethernet cable in each room.
